@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<http://example.org/tio-instance/FS-D01/intent> a icm:Intent .
<http://example.org/tio-instance/FS-D01/exp-del> a icm:DeliveryExpectation ;
